The program is designed to run until 2030. Individual priorities and objectives may be adjusted over time. Two of the key results (access to Employee Assistance Program and 30% improvement in the global accident rate (LTIFR)) have also been incorporated into the DEGREE sustainability framework in the field of action Employability.1

